 />\n我希望大家唔好怕任何野，如果係同路人，就呼籲佢地616再出黎；非同路人，就share長輩圖出去轟炸，起碼一定吸引到藍絲廢老去睇。無需要再多的口角，係廢老親人點都會睇下你send乜野黎，每日分三次share，一點一滴慢慢可能就改變到佢地。"},{"pid":"5f4e90b8080df6a37aac2d21cd1e5b735e4412f2","tid":1218172,"uid":51088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:04:33.000Z","msg":"文宣組Channel group：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFSggAmG8zrSjqjZRw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAFSggAmG8zrSjqjZRw&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWYZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=6edd4cf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFSggAmG8zrSjqjZRw</a><br />\n收到圖既大家可以大肆宣傳/forward <br />\n<br />\n印刷組：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMTlIRIY2lxXgWYPH2CfRg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMTlIRIY2lxXgWYPH2CfRg&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWYZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=fc7abd97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMTlIRIY2lxXgWYPH2CfRg</a><br />\n可幫手派單張同印刷人任<br />\n<br />\n印刷品合集：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEbHMcK94n0le9bTqg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEbHMcK94n0le9bTqg&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWYZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=a411475f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEbHMcK94n0le9bTqg</a><br />\n任拎唔嬲，自己印自己派"},{"pid":"0533aae9298d268134c42dcfa870e302b32e0646","tid":1218172,"uid":200021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:06:34.000Z","msg":"有無人擺街站宣傳？<br />\n我身邊的人都唔太清楚星期日遊行<br />\n要靠我不停send相先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家出街食飯可以傾下遊行嘅野<br />\n俾身邊嘅人可以知多啲<br />\n唔係個個都有上連登 ig"},{"pid":"6454171fd350c33f6fd085fa637216cbf0bf8753","tid":1218172,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:07:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/